des: "Simply stir SwansonÂ® Seasoned Chicken Broth with Roasted Garlic into baking mix along with shredded Cheddar cheese for flavorful, flaky biscuits every time."
ins:

Mix baking mix, cheese and broth to form a soft dough. Drop by spoonfuls onto ungreased baking sheets, making 24.
